{"tid":1471827,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[FO4] 打壓，打壓從未停止","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:19:54.000Z","uid":55589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12cac54ae2213ecb38a805bf32e62ddae096c3ca","tid":1471827,"uid":55589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"BGM：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THYbNAmlwP0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTHYbNAmlwP0&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=01760240\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THYbNAmlwP0</a><br />\n<br />\n打壓，打壓從未停止。<br />\n<br />\n1989年，我老竇參加過百萬人大遊行。透過電視機，心懷希望會見到中國擁抱民主，睇到自由之花盛放嘅一日。可惜，事與願違。<br />\n<br />\n六月四日，中共政府派出解放軍，開槍、坦克⋯ 將基於人性所追求嘅一切都一一摧毀。嗰陣全世界都睇到呢場大屠殺。幾年後，奇怪嘅事就發生⋯<br />\n<br />\n坊間開始散播中共會改變，變得開明，實現民主改革嘅大中華思想。隨住時代更替，科技、娛樂、經濟，加上思想滲透之快，令香港人逐漸忘記中共嘅黑歷史。<br />\n<br />\n但之後，喺 2014年，我哋從港共政府施政中覺醒。多年損害港人利益嘅政策，社會資源分配不當，遺禍後世嘅制度。香港嘅自治權原來早就被侵蝕，「一國兩制」只係一個笑話。<br />\n<br />\n今年 2019年，中共嘅威脅變本加厲。我驚，為父母、為老婆、為仔女嘅未來而恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n因為我喺香港成長中知道一件事，就係：打壓，打壓從未停止。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFallout 4 原版 intro speech：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EM3Y6uw6FtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEM3Y6uw6FtU&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=55a5b4e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EM3Y6uw6FtU</a>"},{"pid":"5ad987b5f7e6538be4a0c08ebc804b5f876b13d2","tid":1471827,"uid":55589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"Ending speech：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l8PsRfU2-V8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl8PsRfU2-V8&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3dxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=d275b770\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l8PsRfU2-V8</a><br />\n<br />\n我感覺到右眼傳嚟嘅痛楚，煙霧、槍聲、流血⋯ 恐懼。無情嘅鎮壓再次推進。我忍住痛嘗試企起身，睇住速龍走嚟捉住我，我已經心中有數，往後嘅人生都將會改寫。<br />\n<br />\n唔理你準備好未，你所規劃嘅人生都會一瞬間走樣。生於亂世，總要面對呢種事。呢個唔係我想要嘅人生，但我責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n香港，我哋嘅屋企。撕裂過後，又再團結一致。<br />\n<br />\n我以為⋯  我有諗過同屋企人可以自欺欺人噉正常過生活。但依家我明白，我知道已經冇得返轉頭。我知道香港已經變咗，前面嘅路會更加難行。<br />\n<br />\n今次，我已經準備好，因為我知道打壓⋯ 打壓從來冇停過。"},{"pid":"94004f29fb5372aa99faa4ccefeec580992abb55","tid":1471827,"uid":55589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"816 撳錢！撳錢！撳錢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oac0qQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foac0qQ8.jpg&h=01be8a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=ecc06d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuyu3CP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyuyu3CP.jpg&h=b13787a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBonEa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBonEa9.png&h=8b3ddeb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWfmahS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWfmahS.jpg&h=a516142e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}